import React from 'react' import {useSelector,useDispatch} from 'react-redux' export default function Metatable() { const event=useSelector((state) => state.dataReducer.selectedEventMeta[0]) return (
{ Boolean(event.dbConnectionId)&&(event.type==="TRANSACTIONAL")&& <> } {event.ingestionStrategy&& } {event.sourceType&& }
Tenant {event.tenantId}
Table Name {event.name}
Table Type {event.type}
Inception Date {event.inceptionDate}
Description {event.description}
DB Name {event.NewDbName}
DB Instance {event.NewDbInstance}
Rollup Column {event.rollupColumn==="null"? "":event.rollupColumn}
Ordering Column {event.orderingColumn==="null"? "":event.orderingColumn}
Write Mode {event.writeMode==="null"? "":event.writeMode}
Session Type {event.sessionType==="null"? "":event.sessionType}
Refresh Frequency {(event.type==="COMPUTED"||event.refreshFrequency!=="null"||event.refreshFrequency!=="NEVER")? "DAILY":"NEVER"}
Data available till {(event.lastSyncTime==="null")? "":event.lastSyncTime}
Is Compacted {(event.enableCompaction==1)? "True":"False"}
Partition Type {event.partitionType==="null"? "":event.partitionType}
Has PII {event.hasPII? 'True':'False'}
Ingestion Strategy {event.ingestionStrategy}
sourceType {event.sourceType}
) }
